dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading. City map is axonometric aerial view. Recto: road map of Turkey. Verso: pictorial map of Istanbul. Ancillary map: pictorial map of Turkey. Includes indices of historical monuments, ruins, and important buildings, distance charts, and color photographs.
